data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Castellina subdivision! Enjoy the magnificent screen enclosed patio pool/spa, perfect for enjoying the balmy tropical weather. The open floor plan creates a wonderful entertainment space, while the lakefront location delivers tranquil views. Step inside to discover ceramic tile floors, volume ceilings, & crown molding, creating an ambiance of grandeur. Natural light fills each room, creating an inviting atmosphere. The grand kitchen offers granite island that is perfect for casual dining & entertainment.  Also are granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & a wine cooler. The master bedroom is an owner retreat with a grand bath & large dressing closet.  Comfort with a new A/C system & full impact glass windows.  A must see home for you UPGRADES INCLUDE:

High-end ceiling-installed speakers in most of the rooms for streaming personal entertainment

3 car extended length garage.  

Travertine marble pool deck.

Custom screen enclosure over the pool deck.

Impact glass windows and great room slider.

Unique pool/spa with changeable color-led lighting.

A/C is one year old
